// Set up some colours to use in this file (consult style guide)
const myColours = {
  colour1:       '#008B8B',
  colour2:       '#20B2AA',
  colour3:       '#1E90FF',
  roiRed:        '#941a1d',
  roiCharcoal:   '#262626',
  roiGrey:       '#595959',
  roiWhite:      '#ffffff'
}

// Export all the colours used by the app
export default {
  tabBar:           myColours.colour2,
  tabIcon:          'white',
  tabIconSelected:  myColours.colour1,
  tabLabel:          'white',
  tabLabelSelected:  myColours.colour1,
  errorBackground:  'red',
  errorText:        '#fff',
  warningBackground:'#EAEB5E',
  warningText:      '#666804',
  noticeBackground: myColours.colour2,
  noticeText:       '#fff',
};
